name: Janus Network
additional_notices:
The following token has a variable tax function on the smart contract to change tax rates post deployment.
Do your own research and be careful if you are trading this token.

description.en: Janus Network is a private blockchain for gaming and NFTs. With the increasing number of subnets, it becomes a necessity for Subnet projects to communicate with each other. Janus Network is a solution that combines NFTs in subnets into a single subnet, enabling the buy, sell, management and NFT dex(NYX Protocol).
